    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "A new skink of the genus Subdoluseps (Hardwicke & Gray, 1828) from Peninsular Malaysia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3187529>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3404779>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3187535> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3187529>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A. Subdoluseps malayana sp. nov. (holotype LSUHC 10995) from Teluk Rubiah, Perak, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by L. L. Grismer). B. Subdoluseps herberti (LSUDPC 4851) from Phuket Island, Phuket, Thailand (photo by W. Grossmann). C. Subdoluseps malayana sp. nov. (LSUDPC 10945) from Kampung Pisang, Perak, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by Z. Dzukafly). D. Subdoluseps herberti (LSUHC 11803) from Perlis State Park, Perlis, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by E.S.H. Quah). E. Subdoluseps samajaya from the Sama Jaya Forest Reserve, Kuching, Sarawak, East Malaysia (photo from Karin et al. 2018). F. Juvenile S. malayana sp. nov. (paratype LSUHC 12098) from Bukit Panchor State Park, Penang, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by M. A. Muin)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3187529/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3404779>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Distribution of the species of the Suboluceps herberti group. Branch lengths in the inset do not represent genetic distance." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3404779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3187535>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Forest habitat of Subdoluseps malayana sp. nov. A. Bukit Panchor State Park, Penang, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by M. A. Muin). B. Teluk Rubiah, Perak, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by Z. Dzukafly). C. Kampung Menora along the Slim River, Perak, Peninsular Malaysia (photo by L. L. Grismer)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3187535/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

